Create a new request by class

Source: R/S7_method_request.R
new_request.Rd

Create a new request by class

Usage

new_request(x)

Arguments

x

An object of class proMain, careMain, or openMain

Value

A new request

Examples

careMain("enrollees") |> new_request()
#> <httr2_request>
#> GET
#> https://data.cms.gov/data-api/v1/dataset/2457ea29-fc82-48b0-86ec-3b0755de7515/data-viewer?offset=0&size=5000
#> Body: empty
#> Policies:
#> • throttle_realm: "data.cms.gov"
proMain("affiliations") |> new_request()
#> <httr2_request>
#> GET
#> https://data.cms.gov/provider-data/api/1/datastore/query/27ea-46a8/0?count=false&format=json&keys=true&limit=2000&offset=0&results=true&rowIds=false&schema=false
#> Body: empty
#> Policies:
#> • throttle_realm: "data.cms.gov"
openMain("profile_covered") |> new_request()
#> <httr2_request>
#> GET
#> https://openpaymentsdata.cms.gov/api/1/datastore/query/23160558-6742-54ff-8b9f-cac7d514ff4e/0?count=false&format=json&keys=true&limit=500&offset=0&results=true&rowIds=false&schema=false
#> Body: empty
#> Policies:
#> • throttle_realm: "openpaymentsdata.cms.gov"
